{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1424290/extras/logo-mars-steamok.png?t=1723837773\" /><br><br><strong>MARS 2120</strong> is a metroidvania with engaging melee combat inspired by classics like Super Metroid, Castlevania: Symphony of the Night, or Guacamelee! With the use of special abilities tied to elements like ice, fire, and electricity help Sgt. Anna \u201cThirteen\u201d Charlotte navigate the colony and battle her way through the secrets of Mars<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1424290/extras/2.5.gif?t=1723837773\" /><br><br><strong>Why do humans dream of space exploration? What if that dream goes wrong?</strong><br><br>Follow Sgt. Anna &quot;Thirteen&quot; Charlotte on a space mission to the first human colony on Mars.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1424290/extras/robookbig.gif?t=1723837773\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1424290/extras/aranhaokbig.gif?t=1723837773\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Explore the Martian colony:</strong> discover new biomes, secrets, and numerous threats along the way.<br></li><li><strong>Face your enemies:</strong> perform combos by mixing melee and ranged attacks, as well as special moves.<br></li><li><strong>Use different equipment and abilities:</strong> find upgrades and new skills while exploring the Martian colony.<br></li><li><strong>Engage in epic battles:</strong> from deadly robots to colossal monsters, build your strategies, uncover their weaknesses, and survive!<br></li><li><strong>Play it your way:</strong> with various accessibility options, you can customize the game according to your style and needs.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1424290/extras/Explora\u00e7\u00e3o3.gif?t=1723837773\" /><br><br><strong>ACCESSIBILITY FEATURES:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play audio logs automatically.<br></li><li>Possibility of changing the speed of the game (Time Scale) to adapt to each person's motor response.<br></li><li>Color changes for people with color blindness and their respective intensities.<br></li><li>Options to make it easier to read objectives on the map, so the player never feels lost.<br></li><li>Setting the size, background color and font color of the subtitles.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Experiment I-17","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1424290/f6f64c1779ddf9d9f20b284fce0194ec53d824e1.jpg"},{"name":"Experiment I-17 (encore)","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1424290/c500ef2ada28f1d065c413a19c37012640a26a22.jpg"},{"name":"Experiment F-08","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1424290/8420bd484a8b3574317944a9d2d29f1fd517b8b0.jpg"},{"name":"Experiment G-33","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1424290/cd3d0c5fbc7ff20c3d9375119c57acf1fd53c537.jpg"},{"name":"Security Unit: Crowd Control","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1424290/3f92340d170289861a1545ab0973c0971ffb0752.jpg"},{"name":"Security Unit: Aerial Patrol","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1424290/30d4e77b657ccc3bba01349fcefc8e2773b80506.jpg"},{"name":"Security Unit: Underground","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1424290/f2fbbc20a1189a20e769c04aacab7497da37269c.jpg"},{"name":"Superior A.I.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1424290/b70fdbfd214349c764ebe3eb8fddb7077bd20bb2.jpg"},{"name":"Experiment I-52","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/14